title: Caribbean Crown West Indian Restaurant
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Caribbean, Catering, Trinidadian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers a list of vegan dishes, including pumpkin and dhalpuri roti, aloo pie, banana fritters.  In-house-made drinks are mauby, sorrel, ginger beer and peanut punch, plus other drinks. Homey atmosphere, free Wi-Fi. Breakfast served all day. Free soda with all specials.
